{# Description: Raw copy/paste Jinja monitor template for Spectra LS P5-S02 metadata-domain gate-prep and run-window validation feedback. #}
{# Version: 2026.04.20.7 #}
{# Last updated: 2026-04-20 #}

{# =========================
  P5-S02 Metadata Functionality Monitor (gate-prep safe)
  Purpose: fast live signal for metadata-domain readiness during bounded P5-S02 windows.
  Usage:
    1) Optional refresh actions:
       - spectra_ls.validate_metadata_prep
       - spectra_ls.run_p3_s03_sequence
       - spectra_ls.validate_contracts
    2) Paste/run in Developer Tools -> Template.
    3) Capture output for pre-window / in-window / post-window records.
  ========================= #}

{% set s_target_primary = 'sensor.shadow_active_target' %}
{% set s_target_fallback = 'sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_target' %}
{% set primary_has_attrs = state_attr(s_target_primary, 'route_trace') is not none or state_attr(s_target_primary, 'captured_at') is not none %}
{% set fallback_has_attrs = state_attr(s_target_fallback, 'route_trace') is not none or state_attr(s_target_fallback, 'captured_at') is not none %}
{% set s_target = s_target_primary if primary_has_attrs else (s_target_fallback if fallback_has_attrs else s_target_primary) %}
{% set route_trace = state_attr(s_target, 'route_trace') or {} %}
{% set contract = state_attr(s_target, 'contract_validation') or {} %}
{% set write_controls = state_attr(s_target, 'write_controls') or {} %}
{% set metadata = state_attr(s_target, 'metadata_prep_validation') or {} %}
{% set metadata_trial = write_controls.metadata_trial_last_attempt if write_controls is mapping and write_controls.metadata_trial_last_attempt is defined else {} %}

{% set authority_mode = write_controls.authority_mode if write_controls is mapping and write_controls.authority_mode is defined else 'missing' %}
{% set route_decision = route_trace.decision if route_trace is mapping and route_trace.decision is defined else '' %}
{% set contract_valid = contract.valid if contract is mapping and contract.valid is defined else false %}
{% set missing_required = contract.missing_required if contract is mapping and contract.missing_required is defined else [] %}
{% set unresolved_required = contract.unresolved_required if contract is mapping and contract.unresolved_required is defined else [] %}

{% set metadata_verdict = metadata.verdict if metadata is mapping and metadata.verdict is defined else 'missing' %}
{% set metadata_ready = metadata.ready_for_metadata_handoff if metadata is mapping and metadata.ready_for_metadata_handoff is defined else false %}
{% set metadata_score = metadata.gate_score if metadata is mapping and metadata.gate_score is defined else 'n/a' %}
{% set metadata_missing = metadata.missing_required if metadata is mapping and metadata.missing_required is defined else [] %}
{% set metadata_owner = metadata.metadata_authority_owner if metadata is mapping and metadata.metadata_authority_owner is defined else 'unknown' %}
{% set metadata_cutover_active = metadata.metadata_cutover_active if metadata is mapping and metadata.metadata_cutover_active is defined else none %}
{% set metadata_cutover_block_reason = metadata.cutover_block_reason if metadata is mapping and metadata.cutover_block_reason is defined else '' %}
{% set metadata_trial_status = metadata_trial.status if metadata_trial is mapping and metadata_trial.status is defined else 'never_attempted' %}
{% set metadata_trial_window = metadata_trial.window_id if metadata_trial is mapping and metadata_trial.window_id is defined else '' %}
{% set metadata_trial_requested_mode = metadata_trial.requested_mode if metadata_trial is mapping and metadata_trial.requested_mode is defined else '' %}
{% set metadata_trial_effective_mode = metadata_trial.effective_mode if metadata_trial is mapping and metadata_trial.effective_mode is defined else '' %}
{% set metadata_trial_dry_run = metadata_trial.dry_run if metadata_trial is mapping and metadata_trial.dry_run is defined else none %}
{% set metadata_trial_reason = metadata_trial.reason if metadata_trial is mapping and metadata_trial.reason is defined else '' %}
{% set metadata_trial_corr = metadata_trial.correlation_id if metadata_trial is mapping and metadata_trial.correlation_id is defined else '' %}

{% set unresolved = state_attr(s_target, 'unresolved_sources') or [] %}
{% set mismatches = state_attr(s_target, 'mismatches') or [] %}
{% set captured_at = state_attr(s_target, 'captured_at') | default('', true) %}
{% set captured_ts = as_timestamp(captured_at) if captured_at not in ['', 'unknown', 'unavailable', 'none', none] else none %}
{% set age_s = (as_timestamp(now()) - captured_ts) if captured_ts is not none else none %}
{% set fresh = age_s is not none and age_s <= 300 %}

{% set status = 'PASS' %}
{% if authority_mode != 'legacy' %}
  {% set status = 'WARN' %}
{% endif %}
{% if metadata_verdict == 'FAIL' or not contract_valid or (missing_required | length) > 0 or (unresolved_required | length) > 0 %}
  {% set status = 'FAIL' %}
{% elif metadata_verdict not in ['PASS', 'WARN'] or not fresh or (unresolved | length) > 0 or (mismatches | length) > 0 %}
  {% set status = 'WARN' %}
{% endif %}

{% set readiness = 'NOT_READY' %}
{% if metadata_verdict == 'PASS' and metadata_ready and contract_valid and (missing_required | length) == 0 and (unresolved_required | length) == 0 and fresh and authority_mode == 'legacy' %}
  {% set readiness = 'READY' %}
{% elif metadata_verdict == 'FAIL' or not contract_valid or (missing_required | length) > 0 or (unresolved_required | length) > 0 %}
  {% set readiness = 'BLOCKED' %}
{% elif metadata_verdict == 'WARN' or authority_mode != 'legacy' or not fresh %}
  {% set readiness = 'CAUTION' %}
{% endif %}

### P5-S02 Metadata Functionality Monitor (`spectra_ls`)
- Status: **{{ status }}**
- Metadata readiness: **{{ readiness }}**
- Timestamp: **{{ now() }}**

### Authority + route baseline
- `write_controls.authority_mode`: **{{ authority_mode }}**
- `route_trace.decision`: **{{ route_decision if route_decision != '' else 'n/a' }}**

### Contract gate
- `contract_validation.valid`: **{{ contract_valid }}**
- `contract_validation.missing_required`: **{{ missing_required | length }}**
- `contract_validation.unresolved_required`: **{{ unresolved_required | length }}**

### Metadata gate
- `metadata_prep_validation.verdict`: **{{ metadata_verdict }}**
- `metadata_prep_validation.ready_for_metadata_handoff`: **{{ metadata_ready }}**
- `metadata_prep_validation.gate_score`: **{{ metadata_score }}**
- `metadata_prep_validation.missing_required`: **{{ metadata_missing | length }}**
- `metadata_prep_validation.metadata_authority_owner`: **{{ metadata_owner }}**
- `metadata_prep_validation.metadata_cutover_active`: **{{ metadata_cutover_active if metadata_cutover_active is not none else 'n/a' }}**
- `metadata_prep_validation.cutover_block_reason`: **{{ metadata_cutover_block_reason if metadata_cutover_block_reason != '' else 'n/a' }}**

### Metadata trial audit (P5-S02-M1)
- `write_controls.metadata_trial_last_attempt.status`: **{{ metadata_trial_status }}**
- `window_id`: **{{ metadata_trial_window if metadata_trial_window != '' else 'n/a' }}**
- `requested_mode`: **{{ metadata_trial_requested_mode if metadata_trial_requested_mode != '' else 'n/a' }}**
- `effective_mode`: **{{ metadata_trial_effective_mode if metadata_trial_effective_mode != '' else 'n/a' }}**
- `dry_run`: **{{ metadata_trial_dry_run if metadata_trial_dry_run is not none else 'n/a' }}**
- `reason`: **{{ metadata_trial_reason if metadata_trial_reason != '' else 'n/a' }}**
- `correlation_id`: **{{ metadata_trial_corr if metadata_trial_corr != '' else 'n/a' }}**

### Parity + freshness
- `unresolved_sources`: **{{ unresolved | length }}**
- `mismatches`: **{{ mismatches | length }}**
- Snapshot freshness (<=300s): **{{ fresh }}** (age_s={{ (age_s | round(1)) if age_s is not none else 'n/a' }})

{% if (missing_required | length) > 0 %}
Contract missing required entities:
{% for item in missing_required %}
- `{{ item }}`
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if (unresolved_required | length) > 0 %}
Contract unresolved required entities (present but unresolved):
{% for item in unresolved_required %}
- `{{ item }}`
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if (metadata_missing | length) > 0 %}
Metadata missing required entities:
{% for item in metadata_missing %}
- `{{ item }}`
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if (unresolved | length) > 0 %}
Unresolved parity sources:
{% for item in unresolved %}
- `{{ item }}`
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if (mismatches | length) > 0 %}
Parity mismatches:
{% for item in mismatches %}
- `{{ item }}`
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

### Quick interpretation
{% if readiness == 'READY' %}
- P5-S02 gate-prep is healthy for bounded-window evidence capture.
{% elif readiness == 'CAUTION' %}
- Metadata lane is partially healthy; authority/safety posture is not fully closeout-ready (for example non-legacy authority mode) and should be normalized before treating this as closeout evidence.
{% elif readiness == 'BLOCKED' %}
- Metadata lane is blocked; resolve FAIL conditions before continuing window execution.
{% else %}
- Metadata lane is not yet closeout-ready; capture additional refresh evidence and re-check.
{% endif %}
{% if metadata_owner == 'legacy_contract_surfaces' and metadata_cutover_active is sameas false %}
- Metadata source-of-truth is still **legacy contract surfaces**; component-mode routing does not imply metadata ownership cutover.
{% endif %}

### Suggested refresh actions
- Service: `spectra_ls.validate_metadata_prep`
- Service: `spectra_ls.metadata_write_trial` (start with `dry_run=true` and bounded `window_id`)
- Service: `spectra_ls.run_p3_s03_sequence`
- Service: `spectra_ls.validate_contracts`
